Add to infra/terraform-github/main.tf:
```hcl
resource "github_repository_environment" "pypi" {
  repository  = var.repository
  environment = "pypi"
  reviewers {
    # Add at least one team or user id as required reviewer
    # teams = [data.github_team.release_approvers.id]
  }
  deployment_branch_policy {
    protected_branches     = false
    custom_branch_policies = true
  }
}
```
This makes the approval gate part of the IaC state, detectable via `terraform plan`, and reproducible on repo recreation.
